OL,5,Cfilm
OL,7,FLiverpool's crown court building was
OL,8,Ftransformed into "Gotham Hospital" as
OL,9,Ffilming got underway on the latest DC
OL,10,FStudios film Clayface.
OL,12,FWork began on Saturday 30 August to
OL,13,Ftransform the court on Derby Square in
OL,14,FLiverpool's city centre into the DC
OL,15,FUniverse film set.
OL,17,FDerby Square was littered with
OL,18,Frubbish, fake graffiti had been
OL,19,Fstencilled onto walls and dozens of
OL,20,Ftents had been put up.
