OL,7,FFilming on Derby Square began in the
OL,8,Fmorning of Sunday 31 August, with the
OL,9,Fcrew shooting multiple takes of
OL,10,Fdoctors and a nurse taking a gurney
OL,11,Fout of the back of an ambulance and
OL,12,Fquickly transporting it through the
OL,13,Ffront door.
OL,15,FAn actor with his face heavily
OL,16,Fbandaged and blood staining his bare
OL,17,Fchest was also seen speaking with the
OL,18,Fproduction crew.
