OL,7,FDozens of locals gathered to watch the
OL,8,Fshoot, with some asking the security
OL,9,Fif the man with his face bandaged was
OL,10,Fthe protagonist Clayface. This was not
OL,11,Fconfirmed.
OL,13,FClayface is expected to be released in
OL,14,FSeptember next year, with Deadline
OL,15,Freporting that Tom Rhys Harris would
OL,16,Fbe playing the character in the horror-
OL,17,Fthriller. The film is based on the
OL,18,Fcomic book character which haunts the
OL,19,Ffictional Gotham City.
